Enkidaata too ltung'ana le Yuda


1   Naaitoki Olaitoriani ajoki nanu, “Ore naaji ninye teneitashe Musa o Samuel te dukuya nanu, meibelekenya oltau lai aing'or kulo tung'ana. Taarai ninche meshomo too nkonyek aainei, naa nchoo ninche meshomo! 
2   Ore ake pee kinkilikuan ninche iyie, aajoki, ‘Kaji iyiook kipuo?’ Nijoki iyie ninche, ‘Nji ejo Olaitoriani:

“Ore lelo lo lmeitai nepuo olmeitai,

ore lelo laa ilo lalem nepuo enetii olalem

ore lelo; laa ilo lameyu,

nepuo enetii olameyu,

ore lelo laa ile yararoto nepuo eyararoto.” ’


3  “Kagelaki nanu shumata ninche mpukunot ong'uan oo looidaikie, Olaitoriani ojo: olalem oar, ildien oopolos, olmotonyi lo loing'ang'e o ng'uesi enkop pee emut ninche aaidaikie. 
4   Naa kaitaa nanu ninche entoki naitureisho too nkitoriat pooki enkop tenkaraki ina nataasa Manase olayioni le Hesekia, olaiguanani le Yuda tiatua Yerusalem.


5  “Kaing'ae liking'urrie iyie

oo Yerusalem, arashu kaing'ae likinchiraki iyie?

Kaing'ae oibelekenya aikilikuanu olmabarishoi lino?


6  Kitanya iyie nanu, Olaitoriani ojo,

iton arrinyo siadi;

neaku aaitorioki nanu enkaina ai pee aagilunore naaidaikie iyie,

anaure nanu tenkibooroto engoro ai.


7  Atisila nanu ninche te silet nasilishoreki,

too nkang'itie pooki eina kop;

aishirie nanu ninche, aidaikie nanu iltung'ana kumok;

neitu ninche eibelekenya aaing'uaa nkoitoi enye.


8  Aitaa nanu esiana oo nkolia enye kumok

alang osinyai loo naaiposha;

ayaka nanu noo ng'otonye ilmurran ooti

olainyalani te nkipirata enkolong; aishoo nanu emion o lkirutoto

metadoiki ninche aluam.


9  Ore ina natoiwuo nkera naapishana neiterre;

etadoyie enkolong enye eton aa dama;

eitukurruaki netusulaki.

Ore inkera naatelekutua, naisho metaari to lalem

te dukuya ilmang'ati lenye, Olaitoriani ojo.”

Eing'unyung'unyaka Yeremia Olaitoriani


10  Woi nanu, yieyio lai, amu kitoiwuo nanu, oltung'ani o ekenya okeshare enkop pooki, neitu aisilenisho, kake aadekita ninche pooki. 
11  Metaa nchoo etiu neijia, Olaitoriani, teneitu nanu aaisiaai aitobiraki teneitu nanu aasai iyie terishata oo lmang'ati laainei etii ninche atua enyamali o sina. 
12  Ketii obo oidim atigila esekenkei naing'uaa moikuape o suyai?


13  “Ore karsisisho ino o lchumati lino naa kaisho metarari, metii enkinyang'a, tenkaraki ing'ok inono pooki, tiatua enkop ino pooki. 
14  Kaaisho nanu iyie isiaayia ilmang'ati linono tiatua enkop nimiyiolo, amu ore te engoro ai neinuaaki enkima nayupuyup ntarasi.” 
15  Olaitoriani iyiolo iyie; tadamuaki nanu nikimutan nanu, nintalaku elap tiaalo nanu too laisilisilok laainei. Ore te ng'iriata ino mikiya nanu; tayiolo ajo tenkaraki iyie pee anap imorot. 
16  Enotoki rorei linono, nanya nanu ninche, neaku irorei linono te nanu eng'ida o enchipai oltau lai; amu te nkarna ino aaipotoki nanu, Olaitoriani, Enkai oo lororani. 
17  Eitu nanu aton to lturrur loo looshipa, ang'ida; atotona nanu openy, amu etii apa enkaina ino shumata nanu, amu kimputa nanu engoro. 
18  Kainyoo pee meish emion ai. Nemeishiunoyu olbae lai ketanya eishiunyeki? Itiu iyie te nanu anaa ereyiet nalejisho, anaa nkariak naaishiunye? 
19  Neaku nji ejo Olaitoriani: “Tenishukunye, naang'amu nanu, naa intashe iyie te dukuya nanu. Teniro iyie ina sidai, neme ina nara pesho, nitiu iyie anaa enkutuk ai. 
20  Naa kaaitaa nanu iyie te kulo tung'ana esuntai nasheta osuyai; nikiarare ninche iyie, kake mikimir ninche iyie, Olaitoriani ojo. 
21  Kaakordu nanu iyie aitung'uaa enkaina eilo torrono, naalaku iyie aitung'uaa enkibung'ata eilo lemeeta olng'ur.”

